    "This study fills this gap by systematically testing GPT-3.5's legal reasoning and ChatGPT's drafting capabilities.",
    "The arguments about the potential of legal AI apply to various areas of law.",
    "However, in this study, we focus on securities cases involving cryptocurrencies as an example of the many possible contexts where AI might assist in the legal process.",
